                       <img alt="" height="24" src="//habrastorage.org/r/w32/getpro/habr/avatars/862/3a7/4e4/8623a74e45f1c61974d8ded49256fb67.png" width="24" class="tm-entity-image__pic">
                      </div></a> <span class="tm-user-info__user"><a href="/ru/users/f1ashag/" class="tm-user-info__username"> f1ashag </a> </span></span> <span class="tm-article-snippet__datetime-published"><time datetime="2022-03-09T18:09:13.000Z" title="2022-03-09, 21:09">сегодня в 21:09</time></span>
